title: Podcast: 'Triple Option' talks Week 8 of prep football, looks ahead to Week 9 playoffs
text: Podcast: 'Triple Option' talks Week 8 of prep football, looks ahead to Week 9 playoffs Podcast: 'Triple Option' talks Week 8 of prep football, looks ahead to Week 9 playoffs Prep Football , Sports , Photos Linn-Mar's Reese Phillips (2) throws a pass as Cedar Rapids Kennedy's Dalles Jacobus (60) closes in during a game Oct. 2. Kennedy has clinched the Class 4A District 5 championship. Linn-Mar also is playoff-bound, and earns home field if it beats Cedar Rapids Jefferson on Thursday. (Stephen Mally/The Gazette) Most Popular
